OL,5, Major retailers are slapping rainbows  
OL,6, on products in a bid to cash in on     
OL,7, Pride, LGBTQ+ campaigners have claimed.
OL,9,FThe Queer Emporium said they welcomed  
OL,10,Fthe extra visibility, but said very    
OL,11,Flittle money was going to the community
OL,12,Fand it felt like a "money grab".       
OL,14,FAn activist said there were also       
OL,15,Fconcerns around the exploitation of    
OL,16,Fworkers making merchandise in countries
OL,17,Fwhere it is illegal to be gay.         
OL,19,FPride Cymru said it was "heartening" to
OL,20,Fsee many brands embracing Pride.       
